title: Trades We’d Like to see; Russell Wilson Talk with Michael-Shawn Dugar
itunes:title: Trades We’d Like to see; Russell Wilson Talk with Michael-Shawn Dugar
description:
A room filled with some heroes- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news in the NFL including potential interest from the Browns for Derek Carr, the Cowboys talking about trading La’el Collins, and some other notable cuts around the league. The heroes give out their “trades we’d like to see” before welcoming in the Athletic’s Michael-Shawn Dugar to talk about what went wrong with Russell Wilson in Seattle.
